<div data-role="content" style="padding: 10px;">
    <div style="padding:5px; background-color:white">
        <div style="height:10px; "></div>
        <div style="font-size: x-large; color:#00C54F;">
            巴士预约成功
        </div>
        <div style="height:10px"></div>
        <div style="background-color: #EAEAEA; height: 1px"></div>
        <div style="height:15px"></div>
        {{printDateInChinese reservation.fullDate}} <span style="color:#00C54F">{{reservation.timeInHH_mm}}</span>
        <div style="height:5px;"></div>
        {{reservation.route.startStation}}  <span style="color:#00C54F">开往</span>  {{reservation.route.endStation}}
        <div style="height:5px;"></div>
        途经: {{reservation.route.middleStations}}
        <div style="height:15px;"></div>
        <div style="padding: 5px 0;font-size: larger; background-color: #F2F2F2">
            乘车地点: {{reservation.route.startStationDesc}}
        </div>
        <div style="height:15px"></div>
        车牌: {{reservation.vehicle.licenseTag}}
        <div style="height:5px;"></div>
        司机: {{reservation.vehicle.driverNam}} {{reservation.vehicle.driverContact}}
        <div style="height:5px;"></div>
        统一票价为{{reservation.route.price}}元
    </div>
    <div style="height:20px"></div>
    <div class="div_with_title">
        <h1 class="div_title"><span style="color: #00C54F; background-color: #f9f9f9;"> &nbsp;&nbsp;温馨提示&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></h1>
        1. 请提前安排好出行时间, 班车按时发车,不等候;<br>
        2. 稍候系统会通过微信给您发送预约消息, 请上车时出示此消息; <br>
        3. 乘车地点有"一起巴士"的标识, 如果找不到乘车地点, 请与司机联系询问.
    </div>
    <div style="height:10px"></div>
</div>
<div class="footer_btn" id="btn_cancel_reservation" style="background-color:red">
    取消预约
</div>